(UK)/meta/color}}|[[Sir Thomas Grove, 1st Baronet|Grove]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Unionist Party/meta/color}}\" |[[Sir Thomas Grove, 1st Baronet|\u2192]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" colspan=\"4\" |[[Jacob Pleydell-Bouverie, 6th Earl of Radnor|Pleydell-Bouverie]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" colspan=\"3\" |[[James Archibald Morrison|J. Morrison]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Levi Lapper Morse|Morse]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" colspan=\"3\" |[[Charles Bathurst, 1st Viscount Bledisloe|Bathurst]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Hugh Morrison (UK politician)|H. Morrison]]\n|}\n\n===1918 to 1974===\n{{legend2|{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}|[[Conservative Party (UK)|Conservative]]|border=1px solid #aaaaaa}}\n{{legend2|{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}|[[Labour Party (UK)|Labour]]|border=1px solid #aaaaaa}}\n{{legend2|{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}|[[Liberal Party (UK)|Liberal]]|border=1px solid #aaaaaa}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Constituency\n!1918\n!1922\n!1923\n!1924\n!''27''\n!1929\n!''31''\n!1931\n!''34''\n!1935\n!''42''\n!''43''\n!1945\n!1950\n!1951\n!1955\n!1959\n!''62''\n!''64''\n!1964\n!''65''\n!1966\n!''69''\n!1970\n|-\n|[[Chippenham (UK Parliament constituency)|Chippenham]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Conservative/meta/color}}\" |[[George Terrell|Terrell]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Alfred James Bonwick|Bonwick]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" colspan=\"8\" |[[Victor Alexander Cazalet|Cazalet]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" colspan=\"6\" |[[David Eccles, 1st Viscount Eccles|Eccles]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" colspan=\"7\" |[[Daniel Awdry|Awdry]]\n|-\n|[[Westbury (UK Parliament constituency)|Westbury]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Conservative/meta/color}}\" |[[George Llewellen Palmer|Palmer]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{